Package: text2vec
Type: Package
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2016-01-31
Title: Fast Text Mining Framework - Vectorization and Word Embeddings
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Description: Very fast and memory-friendly tools for text vectorization and
    state-of-the-art word embeddings (GloVe). Package provides source-agnostic
    streaming API, which allows to perform analysis of collections
    of documents, which are much larger than available RAM.
    All core functions can benefit from multicore machines.
